Package emotionalsongs.java.util

Class Playlist

java.lang.Object
emotionalsongs.java.util.Playlist
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Playlist extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an object Playlist. It has its Id, the Id of the user who created it, an icon, its name and a list of songs
Author:
